"{\"uid\": \"skynews.com.au-australia-news-sport-comedian-arj-barker-stands-up-for-australian-bgirl-raygun-amid-relentless-criticism-over-paris-olympics-performance-news-story-0d3e6b50afb21bcc9c1378e4b9f67a66\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Australian B-girl Rachael 'Raygun' Gunn has received public support from a popular comedian, who lauded her Olympics performance as \\\"pretty courageous\\\".\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9972634753001495, \"rank\": 0.0026944043705265748, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 18, \"end\": 25, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999717152603148, \"rank\": 2.8285531556389794e-05, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 27, \"end\": 33, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.5728883110151916e-24, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}, {\"begin\": 35, \"end\": 39, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9831149677541856, \"rank\": 0.011949807446849186, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Viral Australian breakdancer Rachael 'Raygun' Gunn has received support from an unlikely source, with US comedian Arj Barker standing up for her outing at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 154, \"to\": 328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 160, \"end\": 170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9972634753001495, \"rank\": 0.0026944043705265748, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 183, \"end\": 190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999717152603148, \"rank\": 2.8285531556389794e-05, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 192, \"end\": 198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.5728883110151916e-24, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}, {\"begin\": 200, \"end\": 204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9831149677541856, \"rank\": 0.011949807446849186, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 256, \"end\": 258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9449745100156418, \"rank\": 0.04683875319924382, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 268, \"end\": 278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arj_Barker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Arj Barker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arj_Barker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arj_Barker\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Raygun's performance at the 2024 Olympic Games turned heads globally, as her quirky form of breakdancing - which included bouncing around the stage like a kangaroo and doing the sprinkler - left viewers divided.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 330, \"end\": 336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.5728883110151916e-24, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn, who has a PhD in breakdancing and dance culture, was defeated in each of her three pool matches in the first women's Olympic breakdancing competition.\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 543, \"end\": 547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9831149677541856, \"rank\": 0.011949807446849186, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In all of her matches, her opponent was favoured by each of the nine judges in the scoring system.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 36-year-old's dance moves drew heavy criticism and online trolling, with the Australian Olympic Team rallying to support her during the \\\"devastating\\\" backlash she received.\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 882, \"end\": 905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999082215296, \"rank\": 9.17785884744038e-08, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During a recent stand-up gig, Barker, 50, defended Gunn and the originality of her performance, arguing her uniqueness means she will always be remembered.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1030, \"end\": 1034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9831149677541856, \"rank\": 0.011949807446849186, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I saw some memes that were pretty funny, and, I mean, it was pretty surprising what she did, but I do not get all the hate, you know, like, I do not get like, there is a lot of people that are like 'you are a disgrace' and, 'you are a waste of taxpayers money,'\\\" he told the audience at Melbourne's The Comic Lounge.\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1424, \"end\": 1433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9988008476183986, \"rank\": 0.0009152326297697026, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, I do not understand that, because I think at the very least, what she did was pretty courageous.\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You could say what you want about her, but I mean, she knew she wasn't gonna win.\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She f***ing went out in style, man.\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And you know that other breakdancer, the one she was competing against?\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No, you do not,\\\" he added before the crowd laughed and applauded in response.\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn broke her silence on her drama-filled week on Thursday night AEST, releasing a video on her Instagram from Europe, where she is currently understood to be on holiday with her parents and husband Samuel Free.\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 2044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1832, \"end\": 1836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9831149677541856, \"rank\": 0.011949807446849186, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1898, \"end\": 1902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AEST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1929, \"end\": 1938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4463509209174275e-22, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not realise that that would also open the door to so much hate, which has frankly been pretty devastating,\\\" the university lecturer said in her video.\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I worked my butt off preparing for the Olympics and I gave my all, truly.\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am honoured to have been part of the Australian Olympic team and to be a part of breaking's Olympic debut.\\\"\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2321, \"end\": 2344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999531796337878, \"rank\": 4.682255853117194e-05, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The B-girl also condemned allegations over how she came to be selected for Australia's Olympic breaking team after theories emerged online via a petition on Change.org which has since been taken down.\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2593, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2468, \"end\": 2477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.6397470015013601, \"rank\": 0.4475534120119279, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2550, \"end\": 2560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Change.org\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Change.org\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Change.org\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Change.org\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Australian Olympic Committee hit out at the allegations on Thursday, releasing a lengthy statement that outlined the \\\"facts\\\" of how Gunn secured qualification to the Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2595, \"end\": 2609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.207203653853768e-22, \"text\": \"The Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\"}, {\"begin\": 2599, \"end\": 2627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2731, \"end\": 2735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9831149677541856, \"rank\": 0.011949807446849186, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 2774, \"end\": 2779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999967786320257, \"rank\": 3.2213784329285445e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\",